    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This car is a solid performer that has plenty of character and many miles left to offer! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a practical and functional choice for anyone looking for value. With a bit of love, this car will continue to be a reliable companion on the road!",
