    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for a daily driver. The engine runs smoothly without any unusual noises, and the transmission shifts cleanly through all gears. While the exterior shows some minor cosmetic wear typical of its age, the interior remains clean and comfortable. All major systems, including the air conditioning and electronics, are fully functional, providing a dependable and pleasant driving experience.",
